      <title>Drumming in a small club</title>
      <link>https://www.anthonycastaneda.com/posts/drummer-small-room/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Jan 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>anthony@anthonycastaneda.com (Anthony Castañeda)</author>
